Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\c&H82FEFE&\pos(1028,691)}四月25日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方出現8名死傷者的Terra事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處于事件中心的Atsuko Jackson警部此次丑聞曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko警部接受了Monstro Petro及其傘下組織的金錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Ricardo巡查部長的內部檢舉而敗露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事態的發展令人矚目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是很久沒有和觀眾見面的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自Daniela Carneiro Jr的緊急報道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用花言巧語誘騙無家可歸的少年少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這背后的黑暗交易
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔般的馬戲團的恐怖真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將由我Daniel Campbell Jr去揭開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴雨中的起點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 心愛的牛肉罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填滿饑餓的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,te amo（葡語：我愛你）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,te amo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,te amo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,te amo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要的是這個吧 請吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家的話倒是有錢...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話只有這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這自行車買的時候還是挺貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了去拯救一個名為Lita的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追趕馬戲團的善良少年而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我管你是Lita還是Lisa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追馬戲團的話就這樣一直往前走就可以了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\c&HFEEFD1&\pos(108,689)}Sapatos 巧克力馬戲團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,販賣純真兒童的卑鄙馬戲團的傳聞是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對膽敢抵抗的人毫不留情的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣 這鮮淋淋的血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dany 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場感很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok Zoey
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先給馬戲團一個廣角鏡頭 然后我走進盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說完開場白之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走進帳篷時 這個家伙就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 不會有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新鮮的雞血 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會拿到頭條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子頭條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快舉起攝像機！ 這是命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！搞什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回Sao Paraiso
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子我是不會交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會四處散布你的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種赤身裸體的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無修正的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小不點！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我沒看到就可以偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 到外面去發傳單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去拿！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻縫隙間的虛幻世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡情享受近乎瘋狂的興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會在清醒的狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入夢中 進入夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開演了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么？ 你想逃走是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 你不是一個人在戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As 5 horas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大叔我的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 只有真實的報道才能救你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說給我聽的話 這個就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的陰謀、暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你的完整的悲慘遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個只是被袋鼠打的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是袋鼠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是活蹦亂跳的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你被封口了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來是下地獄 不說出來也是下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在此時 你遇到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我必須要拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想到臉上受了傷...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天拍照？ 什么照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\c&HFAEBD7&\pos(1050,695)}四月26日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 大家睡的都好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Michiko大人在問你們睡的好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nuno！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會什么技藝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在照看動物們 還有打掃衛生之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 打掃衛生是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 真的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭 變熊貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nuno
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成熊貓了可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么會...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Michiko Menezes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭條新聞被我抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色情業者Daniela Carneiro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將天真無邪的孩子們作為飼餌的卑鄙惡黨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用攝像機把多少個孩子送下了地獄？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你傷害這些孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕犧牲我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛獸先生 請睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 Daniela先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣很糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一直在打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana好像很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana應該去做廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“味道很好 Hatchin”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“謝謝”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 磨蹭什么 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\pos(241,699)}四月27日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾一下 有新的小鬼要來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部給我丟掉 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 收拾好后就去Madame那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光線很耀眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面 轉到正面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯 今晚你就能去樂園了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是游樂園嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 游樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和別人說話的時候把墨鏡摘下來如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉是怎么回事？ 又打架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你來干什么 我哪里都不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想硬把我拖走？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在電視上的你看起來很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來看看你過得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過得很好 我過得很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件衣服是她的愛好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛 就像踩球的馬戲少女一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去！ 回去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里的Madame也叫Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也叫Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這里的Michiko很溫柔 疼愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我非常討厭你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎 那你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你喜歡的那個Michiko那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了 穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義使者登場！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允許邪惡在這個世界橫行！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是證據！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們被救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了！ 喂！ 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子是誠實的 Daniela
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是壞人分別的很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 你們被騙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來吧 和我一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nuno 放飛氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種天氣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！ 放飛氣球！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 準備完畢 放開繩索！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的證據啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 不會讓你逃掉的！ Michiko Menezes！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 那個就是Michiko！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什么玩笑！ Hatchin！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我流淚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超重了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把這些孩子放下去 還沒拿到錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Menezes！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛獸禁止登船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游樂園什么的是騙人的吧 想把我們賣掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 腦子挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Madame
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長得又白又可愛 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！ 我不會讓你這樣的怪物為所欲為！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mchiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那個女人射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的麻醉彈都是射擊小動物用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小瞧人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人是什么人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的Michiko只有我一個人 給我記牢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 好丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然把我重要的商品...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什么玩笑！ 放馬過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來怎么辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空著手去的話會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在嗎 纏人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 可惡！ 可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了 爬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情好難看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手吧 下面是大海 會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫會有辦法？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 絕對的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 我會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我絕對不會松手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(700,0)\c&H99E6F9&\pos(219,684)}四月28日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭條新聞我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒有什么別的想說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 謝謝你 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我原諒你了 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita？ 你叫Lita嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個戴眼鏡的小鬼在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的男朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惡心了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我們還會見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fad(100,0)\c&H8FBCD0&}待續
