Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.35,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}君のすぐ隣のBest Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.35,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}我是你近在咫尺的Best Friend
